item.title: Engagement with Keppel Infrastructure on 22nd Sep 2022
item.description: Being a student, I hope to learn some necessary skills that can one day be applied. Yet, sometimes I ask myself, what would I do in an unfamiliar situation? I may not have an answer to this, but after listening to others’ experiences, I did gain some insights. I will share three main takeaways. Open-Mind One thing that stood out during the engagement is that the presenters, although all engineering-trained, are all not in technical roles.
